cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper deals with deep learning and convolutional neural networks for breast cancer classification on diffusion-weighted MR images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses domain adaptation, which is a common topic in machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The use of neural networks also suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
